    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 inline-six, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline via six individual throttle bodies. Mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, the drivetrain remains tight with a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential ensuring optimal power distribution. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including subframe reinforcement and a VANOS overhaul, preserving its torsional rigidity and valve timing precision. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, the suspension geometry remains true, and the throttle response is telepathic. A driver-focused machine for those who value mechanical purity and longitudinal G-forces.",
